11:19.554 --> 11:22.682
All right, look, I'm glad
I could help you and Simone.

11:22.682 --> 11:25.018
But we don't have
to force this connection.

11:25.018 --> 11:26.895
Okay.
Yeah, I definitely hear you.

11:26.895 --> 11:28.146
So why don't we
just get a drink,

11:28.146 --> 11:29.314
