tell Simone that we tried?

11:29.314 --> 11:30.565
Yes, yes, let's do that.

11:30.565 --> 11:31.816
- Amir.
- Yeah.

11:31.816 --> 11:33.151
- Two Lambruscos, please.
- Coming right up.

11:33.151 --> 11:38.365
<i>♪ ♪</i>

11:38.365 --> 11:39.699
Here you go, fellas.

11:39.699 --> 11:41.284
- Cheers.
