11:51.336 --> 11:52.754
It's not bad.

11:54.005 --> 11:54.923
Cheers.

11:54.923 --> 11:57.092
<i>[Saweetie's "Best Friend"]</i>

11:57.092 --> 11:59.719
- Another Lambrusco?
- Yeah, another Lambrusco.

11:59.719 --> 12:01.513
I mean, if I could
have one superpower,

12:01.513 --> 12:02.597
it would obviously be...

12:02.597 --> 12:03.807
both: Flight.
Yo.

12:03.807 --> 12:05.183
Another Lambrusco!

12:05.183 --> 12:06.601
The crazy thing
about space...

12:06.601 --> 12:08.061
