12:08.061 --> 12:10.563
Yo!
Another Lambrusco!

12:10.563 --> 12:12.857
Busta Rhymes.
John Coltrane.

12:12.857 --> 12:15.610
Pizza!
Another Lambrusco!

12:15.610 --> 12:17.654
