12:57.360 --> 12:59.362
Mm-mm.
No, no, no.

12:59.362 --> 13:02.699
I am trying to get like you.

13:02.699 --> 13:06.327
No, no, no, I am trying
to get like you, my dude.

13:06.327 --> 13:07.829
[inhales sharply]

13:07.829 --> 13:09.831
both:
I'm trying to get like you!

13:09.831 --> 13:11.416
[whispering]
I'm trying to get like you.

13:11.416 --> 13:12.375
That's it.
That's it.

13:12.375 --> 13:14.544
Aw, yay.

13:14.544 --> 13:17.297
I knew you two would be friends
sooner rather than later.

13:17.297 --> 13:18.715
Simone,
you were totally right.

13:18.715 --> 13:20.675
Oh, we should invite Courtney
to Wyatt's potluck.

13:20.675 --> 13:23.386
Courtney, you gotta come over
tonight to Wyatt's potluck.

13:23.386 --> 13:24.763
- I'm down.
- [chuckles]

13:24.763 --> 13:26.598
I'm, like,
on the ocean floor.

13:26.598 --> 13:28.725
You know
what I love about the ocean?

13:28.725 --> 13:30.769
- The waves.
- The waves, yeah.

13:30.769 --> 13:33.063
<i>♪ ♪</i>

13:33.063 --> 13:34.606
[phone buzzing]

13:36.858 --> 13:38.568
So...

13:38.568 --> 13:40.737
I wanted to talk to you
about moving in.

13:40.737 --> 13:42.572
- Oh, Anthony, you don't have--
- No, no, no, no.

13:42.572 --> 13:44.240
I was a little
thrown off before,

13:44.240 --> 13:45.950
but we've got
a good thing going.

13:45.950 --> 13:48.036
