you wanted to do it right now.

13:48.036 --> 13:49.245
But I can definitely see us

13:49.245 --> 13:51.164
moving in together
in the future.

13:51.164 --> 13:52.749
Thank you for saying that.

13:52.749 --> 13:55.293
I was a little in my head about
it 'cause you know, it's--

13:55.293 --> 13:57.379
- Yeah, yeah, yeah, I know.
- Okay.

13:59.130 --> 14:02.509
<i>♪ ♪</i>

14:02.509 --> 14:06.179
Ooh, this may be
my best jerk chicken yet!

14:06.179 --> 14:07.430
Okurrrrr?

14:07.430 --> 14:08.890
Okurrrrr!

14:08.890 --> 14:09.974
Honey, no.

14:09.974 --> 14:12.769
We talked about that.
Don't do that.

14:12.769 --> 14:15.397
Hey, y'all.
I brought fried chicken.

14:15.397 --> 14:16.523
More chicken.

14:16.523 --> 14:18.191
See, this is why I asked y'all

14:18.191 --> 14:19.943
