what you're bringing.

14:19.943 --> 14:21.152
Calm down, Wyatt.

14:21.152 --> 14:23.780
- It's not that much chicken.
- Yo, yo, yo.

14:23.780 --> 14:25.949
- I brought chicken.
- Great.

14:25.949 --> 14:26.991
What y'all drinking?

14:26.991 --> 14:30.245
Just some
Jones & Sons Peach Wine.

14:30.245 --> 14:32.580
- Everyone loves it.
- Oh, wonderful.

14:32.580 --> 14:34.791
Everybody's
drinking my wine, huh?

14:34.791 --> 14:36.960
<i>This is a disaster!
Everyone's drinking my wine!</i>

14:36.960 --> 14:38.086
Yeah, it was my idea.

14:38.086 --> 14:39.921
I brought it over earlier
to surprise you.

14:39.921 --> 14:41.840
Oh,
and what a lovely surprise.

14:41.840 --> 14:43.633
Hey.
How did you get in my place?

14:43.633 --> 14:45.301
- Oh, Anthony let me in.
- Nice.

14:45.301 --> 14:47.429
- He just let you in.
- Yes.

14:47.429 --> 14:48.972
<i>Damn you, Anthony!</i>

14:48.972 --> 14:50.515
Are you okay, Sherm?

14:50.515 --> 14:52.225
- You're sweating.
- Oh, I'm fine.

14:52.225 --> 14:53.643
<i>Oh, no.
I'm sweating.</i>

14:53.643 --> 14:55.687
<i>Is it the nerves,
or is it the botulism?</i>

14:55.687 --> 14:57.522
<i>Nicky was staring at me.
Does she know my secret?</i>

14:57.522 --> 14:59.065
<i>Maybe she's not looking anymore.</i>

14:59.065 --> 15:00.734
<i>Oh, no, she's still looking!
The jig is up!</i>

15:00.734 --> 15:02.318
Sherm,
are you sure you're okay?

15:02.318 --> 15:03.570
Yes, yes, I'm fine.

15:03.570 --> 15:04.571
Can I holla at you
over here real quick?

15:04.571 --> 15:05.488
- Yeah, sure.
- Thank you.

15:05.488 --> 15:06.656
Ooh, you're sweating hard.

15:06.656 --> 15:09.200
Hey.
Well, here's the deal.

15:09.200 --> 15:11.369
That wine I made may be
poisoned with botulism.

15:11.369 --> 15:12.871
Wait, wait.
You poisoned me?

15:12.871 --> 15:14.539
Maybe poisoned you. Maybe.

15:14.539 --> 15:15.707
How could you
not say anything?

15:15.707 --> 15:16.958
