like this!

15:16.958 --> 15:18.418
You could have poisoned
everybody here!

15:18.418 --> 15:19.711
You maybe poisoned
all these people here.

15:19.711 --> 15:20.962
You brought that wine here
without telling me.

15:20.962 --> 15:23.214
Oh, I was just trying
to be a fun friend.

15:23.214 --> 15:24.507
Well, you were wrong,

15:24.507 --> 15:25.967
and now we're both stuck
in this hell together.

15:25.967 --> 15:27.510
There's a chance
everything's still okay.

15:27.510 --> 15:28.928
Mm, so we can't
say anything now.

15:28.928 --> 15:30.680
And we won't
say anything now.

15:30.680 --> 15:33.183
- Okay, mm.
- [clears throat]

15:33.183 --> 15:35.393
<i>♪ ♪</i>

15:35.393 --> 15:36.853
What's up, y'all?

15:36.853 --> 15:39.105
We brought y'all
some chicken fingers.

15:40.190 --> 15:41.232
Fantastic.

15:41.232 --> 15:42.901
[chuckles]

15:42.901 --> 15:43.985
Hey, hey.

15:43.985 --> 15:45.528
Brought y'all
some vegan chicken.

15:45.528 --> 15:47.447
Even our vegan option
is chicken.

15:47.447 --> 15:48.740
And you know why?

15:48.740 --> 15:51.034
Because nobody texted me
what they're bringing.

15:52.952 --> 15:54.704
Noah.

15:54.704 --> 15:56.539
- Boy, I am lit.
- Nice.

15:56.539 --> 15:58.875
I'm starting to sober up,
but I love that for you.

15:58.875 --> 16:01.836
Hey, hey.
I got to apologize to you.

16:01.836 --> 16:03.630
I was definitely
being a jerk earlier,

16:03.630 --> 16:06.341
but the reason is I...

16:06.341 --> 16:07.884
- Nah, I got to chill.
- Nah, man.

16:07.884 --> 16:09.803
We're like family now.
What's up?

16:09.803 --> 16:11.846
Okay.

16:11.846 --> 16:13.556
I was a jerk to you earlier,

16:13.556 --> 16:14.683
but the reason is...

16:14.683 --> 16:16.893
♪ I'm in love with Simone ♪

16:16.893 --> 16:18.728
Oh, yeah, I definitely wish
you didn't say that.

16:18.728 --> 16:22.440
Ooh, so what are you two
bonding over now?

16:22.440 --> 16:24.651
I was just telling Noah...

16:24.651 --> 16:26.403
that I'm in love with you.

16:26.403 --> 16:27.654
And he said it again.

16:27.654 --> 16:30.490
Stop the potluck!

16:32.867 --> 16:34.327
I...

16:34.327 --> 16:37.539
am in love with this woman!

16:37.539 --> 16:38.748
[all gasp]

16:44.587 --> 16:45.547
Simone, you are
the love of my life.

16:47.382 --> 16:49.718
And it's always been you.

16:49.718 --> 16:51.219
- So what do you say?
- Hey, man.

16:51.219 --> 16:53.346
I think you may be
a little intoxicated right now.

16:53.346 --> 16:55.765
Yeah, and I've never
seen you that way, Courtney.

16:55.765 --> 16:57.350
So what are you gonna do,
just pick this old

16:57.350 --> 16:58.893
broccoli head-ass boy over me?

16:58.893 --> 16:59.978
Hey.

16:59.978 --> 17:01.396
I think you should leave, Courtney.

17:01.396 --> 17:02.981
How could you not see
that I've always loved you?

17:02.981 --> 17:05.817
I mean, I married you,
and it wasn't

17:05.817 --> 17:08.570
to help this old string bean
head-ass boy over here.

17:08.570 --> 17:09.904
- Yikes.
- Simone.

17:09.904 --> 17:11.740
Come on.
He's not worthy of you.

17:11.740 --> 17:13.491
Yeah, he's tall,
but he is goofy.

17:13.491 --> 17:15.243
- Mm-hmm.
- Look at this bok choy body.

17:15.243 --> 17:17.495
Bok choy--hey, man, stop
comparing me to vegetables.

17:17.495 --> 17:18.997
I wish somebody
brought some vegetables.

17:18.997 --> 17:20.623
Look, I'm not
about to just stand here

17:20.623 --> 17:22.000
and let you continue
to disrespect me

17:22.000 --> 17:23.835
with
your Potato Head-looking ass.

17:23.835 --> 17:26.171
No, not a good got, man.
I taught you better than that.

17:26.171 --> 17:27.505
- So what you wanna do, then?
- What you wanna do, then?

17:27.505 --> 17:28.673
I asked first.

17:28.673 --> 17:29.966
You tell me
what you're gonna do,

17:29.966 --> 17:31.676
and then I'll tell you
what I'm going to do.

17:31.676 --> 17:32.886
No, I'ma tell you
what you're gonna do.

17:32.886 --> 17:34.471
You're gonna just leave,
just go, just leave.

17:34.471 --> 17:37.599
All right, I'll leave.
Come on, Sim-Sim.

17:37.599 --> 17:38.725
We don't need this mess.
Let's go.

17:38.725 --> 17:40.310
