17:40.310 --> 17:41.561
I'm staying with Noah.

17:43.313 --> 17:45.440
All right.

17:45.440 --> 17:47.942
But I want a divorce.

17:47.942 --> 17:50.278
Good luck staying
in the country.

17:50.278 --> 17:51.863
That's messed up.

17:51.863 --> 17:54.074
- Mm-mm, go that way.
- Nuh-uh, uh-uh.

17:54.074 --> 17:55.658
There you go.

17:55.658 --> 17:58.787
<i>[somber music]</i>

17:58.787 --> 18:01.414
Wow, I did not know
he felt like that.

18:01.414 --> 18:03.541
- [sighs]
- And I'm so embarrassed.

18:03.541 --> 18:05.168
I'm sorry, Noah.

18:05.168 --> 18:06.711
Don't be.

18:06.711 --> 18:09.255
That's on Courtney,
not you.

18:09.255 --> 18:11.508
You don't think I look like
all those vegetables, right?

18:11.508 --> 18:13.009
- No, no, not at all.
- Okay.

18:13.009 --> 18:14.552
Just wanted
to nip that in the bud.

18:14.552 --> 18:16.680
- Yeah.
- [clears throat]

18:16.680 --> 18:19.933
I really love
being with you, Noah.

18:19.933 --> 18:22.352
I really love
being with you too.

18:22.352 --> 18:24.854
I guess when your girlfriend

18:24.854 --> 18:27.190
has a husband that's
actually in love with her,

18:27.190 --> 18:29.609
