to be some issues.

18:29.609 --> 18:31.152
Yeah.
[chuckles]

18:31.152 --> 18:32.529
Yeah.

18:32.529 --> 18:34.739
So...

18:34.739 --> 18:36.533
what are we gonna do?

18:36.533 --> 18:39.828
<i>♪ ♪</i>

18:39.828 --> 18:41.705
Hey, everybody.

18:41.705 --> 18:44.082
